      "text": [
        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"إِنَّمَا اَلنِّسَاءُ عِيٌّ وَ عَوْرَةٌ فَاسْتُرُوا اَلْعَوْرَةَ بِالْبُيُوتِ وَ اُسْتُرُوا اَلْعِيَّ بِالسُّكُوتِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4372 - Imam (as) said:\n\"Indeed, women are a source of dependence and vulnerability. So, conceal their vulnerability within the homes and cover their dependence with silence.\""
        ]
      }
    },
